sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client as Consumidor / Aplicación
    participant API as API Collections Retrieve - Product <br/> Epica 65964: ConsultaCobranzasH2H <br/> HU 66016 <br/> ms-rc-col-collections_retrieve-product
    participant CL as Caché Local
    participant Param as Lib Regionalizacion <br/> lib-java-webflux_core-xrs v. 2.4.2-SNAPSHOT
    participant Lib as Librería Pipeline (ConfigMap)
    participant wrapper as Wrapper Abanks Multiconexión <br/> SP: HTH_P_CONS_CAMPOS_CBR_X_SERV <br/> ConnectionProxyAbanksHN
    participant Errors as Lib Errores <br/> lib-java-webflux_core-xrs v. 2.4.2-SNAPSHOT

    Note over Client, Errors: Flujo Honduras (HN01) - Consulta Campos Cobranza por Servicio

    Client->>API: GET /collateral-administration/collections-retrieves/v1/retrieve-collection-field
    Note right of Client: Headers: <br/> Source-Bank, Destination-Bank, <br/> Caller-Service, Authorization, <br/> Application-Id <br/> Query Params: <br/> serviceId, operationType

    rect rgb(250, 250, 250)
    Note over API, Client: Validación Campos Obligatorios
    API->>API: Validación Esquema OpenAPI
    API->>API: Validar Headers obligatorios <br/> Source-Bank, Authorization, Application-Id
    alt Errores de validación
        API-->>Client: Error 400 Bad Request
    end
    end

    rect rgb(250, 250, 250)
    Note over Client, Param: Proceso Validacion Regional
    API->>API: Cache Local <br/> key: collection-retrieve

    alt Consulta parámetros en caché local

        API->>CL: Consultar parámetros de Lib Regionalizacion en caché local
        Note right of API: Domain: "COLLECTION_RETRIEVE" <br/> name: "RETRIEVE-COLLECTION-FIELD" <br/> country: XRS

        CL->>API: Obtiene parámetros de Lib Regionalizacion en Caché Local

    else Cache MISS - Consulta Lib Regionalizacion

        API->>Param: Consultar parámetros en Lib Regionalizacion
        Note right of API: Domain: "COLLECTION_RETRIEVE" <br/> name: "RETRIEVE-COLLECTION-FIELD" <br/> country: XRS

        Param->>API: Obtiene parámetros Lib Regionalizacion

        API->>CL: Guarda parámetros en caché local (TTL 24h)

    end

    API->>API: Validar Servicio Regional
    Note over API: Regiones Disponibles de Dynamo: <br/> HN01-HN01

    alt Región no encontrada o enabled: false
        API-->>Client: Error 422 (REGION_NOT_CONFIGURED / REGION_NOT_ENABLED)
    end
    end

    Note over API: Uso del Patrón Strategy
    API->>API: Selecciona Estrategia por Source-Bank

    alt Source-Bank = HN01



        API->>Lib: Consulta Constantes
        Lib->>API: Retorna constantes necesarias
        Note left of Lib: Constantes: <br/> caller-service <br/> schema <br/> package <br/> procedureName <br/> connectionType <br/> operationType

        note over API, wrapper: Paso 1: Consultar campos de cobranza por servicio y operación

        API->>API: Preparar Payload
        Note over API: connection.paramName = libparam.param-name <br/> secretName = libparam.secret-name <br/> connectionType = const.connectionType <br/> params.PV_IDSERVICIO = serviceId <br/> params.PV_OPERACION = operationType

        API->>wrapper: CALL PROXYABANKSHM.HTH_P_CONS_CAMPOS_CBR_X_SERV
        Note over wrapper: Host: ConnectionProxyAbanksHN <br/> Schema: PROXYABANKSHM <br/> SP: HTH_P_CONS_CAMPOS_CBR_X_SERV

        wrapper->>API: Response SP: HTH_P_CONS_CAMPOS_CBR_X_SERV

        API->>API: Evaluar Payload
        Note over API: OUT: Pt_CamposPorServicio (array) <br/> Pv_CodigoMensaje (SUCCESS / ERROR) <br/> Pv_DescripcionMensaje

        alt If PV_CODIGOMENSAJE != SUCCESS
            wrapper-->>API: Error response
            Note over API: BusinessCoreException(apiMethod, applicationBackend, errorMessage, errorCode)
            API-->>Client: Error HTTP 4XX / 5XX
        else If PV_CODIGOMENSAJE == SUCCESS

            API->>API: Construir Response
            Note over API: Mapeo Campos Response: <br/> data.collectionFieldList[].originField = CAMPO_ORIGEN <br/> data.collectionFieldList[].destinationPosition = POS_DESTINO

            API->>Client: Response Exitoso
            Note over Client, API: HTTP 200 <br/> data.collectionFieldList[].originField <br/> data.collectionFieldList[].destinationPosition

        end

    end

    Note over Client, Errors: Flujo Alternativo - Error
    activate API
    alt Exception occurs
        note over Errors: Error Library Handler
        activate Errors
            API->>Errors: BusinessCoreException(apiMethod, applicationBackend, errorMessage, errorCode)
            Errors-->>API: Retorna httpCode, businessErrorCode, shortDesc, longDesc
        deactivate Errors
        activate Client
            API-->>Client: Retorna error
        deactivate Client
        Note over Client,Errors: Diagrama guía de manejo de errores <br/> http://bit.ly/4rpKVIU
    end
    deactivate API
